Susan Olsen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Susan_Olsen 0 Susan Marie Olsen (born August 14, 1961) is an American actress, animal welfare advocate, artist, and former radio host. Olsen is known for her role as Cindy Brady, the youngest Brady child in the sitcom The Brady Bunch for the full run of the show, from 1969 to 1974. In 1995 she had a minor role in The Brady Bunch Movie as a reporter. Susan_Marie_Olsen ( born August_14 , 1961 ) is an_American_actress , animal_welfare_advocate , artist , and former_radio_host .
